body:
First, create empty lib crate.

```bash
cargo init --lib foo
```

With `use crate::foo::bar`:

```rust
//! Hello
//!
//! ```
//! use crate::foo::bar;
//! bar();
//! ```

#[cfg(doctest)]
pub fn bar ()
{
  println!("hello");
}
```

